{"word":"περιγληνάομαι","slug":"περιγληνάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n81193\" key=\"periglhna/omai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">περιγλην-άομαι</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">γλήνη</etym>) <sense id=\"n81193.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">turn round the eyeballs, glare around</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περιγληνώμενος ὄσσοις</foreign>, of a lion, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:25:241\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.241</biblScope></bibl>. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ής, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype></foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having eyes all round</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τροχαλόν</foreign>, i.e. the Milky Way, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:476\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">476</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}